    The GameProgress class extends DataManager to provide methods for retrieving and updating game progress data from a CSV file.

    The Inventory class extends DataManager to provide methods for retrieving and updating inventory data from a CSV file.

    The ParentalControls class extends DataManager to manage parental control settings for players, including playtime limits and playtime statistics.

    The Player class extends DataManager to provide specific methods for retrieving and updating player-related data from a CSV file.

    The Store class extends Inventory and provides methods to manage a player's store inventory and pricing data.
    Timestamp
    The Timestamp class represents a timestamp with both formatted string representation and Unix time (epoch seconds).

    The Transactions class extends DataManager to provide methods for retrieving and updating transaction data from a CSV file.
